---
layout : base.njk
title : Eliminate Waste and Recycling Equipment Headaches
---
<main id="main" class="bg-gray-100">
    <div class="bg-secondary-light">
        <div class="container mx-auto p-6 text-center text-gray-900">
            <h1 class="my-4 text-4xl">Frustrated by trash pile-up, odor, and high costs for waste removal?</h1>
            <p class="leading-normal mb-4 text-xl">
                Our customers save money, reduce odor, and have freedom from their current hauler’s sub-par equipment. They can focus on
                the work that makes their business succeed.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center py-16 space-x-6">
                <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                    Call Us
                </a>
                <a class="button" href="/contact/">
                    Get Information
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl text-center">How We Help you</h2>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap my-6 lg:-mx-6">
                <div class="w-full mb-4 lg:w-1/3 lg:px-6">
                    <div class="block h-full bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8 shadow-md">
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <div class="h-80 lg:h-48 bg-cover bg-top text-center overflow-hidden"
                            style="background-image: url('/static/help-you-cards/rental.jpg')"></div>
                            <div class="px-4 pt-4">
                                <h2 class="text-xl text-center mb-2">Nationwide Rental Programs</h2>
                                <p>
                                    Rent a commercial waste compactor from ARC, and get the peace of mind that comes with best-in-class service included.
                                    Our expert local installers will guide your setup and staff training.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full mb-4 lg:w-1/3 lg:px-6">
                    <div class="block h-full bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8 shadow-md">
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <div class="h-80 lg:h-48 bg-cover bg-top text-center overflow-hidden"
                            style="background-image: url('/static/help-you-cards/purchase.jpg')"></div>
                            <div class="px-4 pt-4">
                                <h2 class="text-xl text-center mb-2">Purchase Programs</h2>
                                <p>
                                    Buy a commercial waste compactor from ARC and let our expertise guide your installation.
                                    Use our responsive local service whenever you have need.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full mb-4 lg:w-1/3 lg:px-6">
                    <div class="block h-full bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8 shadow-md">
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <div class="h-80 lg:h-48 bg-cover bg-top text-center overflow-hidden"
                            style="background-image: url('/static/help-you-cards/service.jpg')"></div>
                            <div class="px-4 pt-4">
                                <h2 class="text-xl text-center mb-2">Service & Maintenance</h2>
                                <p>
                                    Hire us for responsive local service, 6-month preventative maintenance, and on-demand repairs.
                                    When you buy from us, you get access to the same trusted services.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white shadow-md">
        <div class="container text-center text-gray-900">
            <h2 class="text-2xl">
                Waste haulers should not trap their customers with a service that allows waste to pile up,
                odors to become a problem, and equipment to remain broken down.
            </h2>

            <div class="flex justify-center py-6 space-x-6">
                <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                    Call Us
                </a>
                <a class="button" href="/contact/">
                    Get Information
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto p-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl text-center">Industry Applications</h2>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-12">
            {% for application in applications %}
            <div class="w-1/2 lg:w-1/5 my-6 text-center">
                <img src="/static/applications/{{ application.image }}" class="rounded-full mx-auto shadow-md w-20 h-20 md:w-40 md:h-40">
                <h3 class="text-lg mt-4">{{ application.name }}</h3>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>

     <div class="py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl text-center">Products</h2>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center my-6 lg:-mx-6">
                {% for product in products %}
                <div class="w-full mb-6 px-6 lg:w-1/3">
                    <a href="/products" class="block h-full bg-white rounded-lg text-gray-900 no-underline overflow-hidden mb-8 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <div class="h-80 lg:h-48 bg-cover bg-top text-center overflow-hidden"
                            style="background-image: url('/static/product-cards/{{ product.image }}')"></div>
                            <div class="px-4 pt-4">
                                <h2 class="text-xl text-center mb-2">{{ product.name }}</h2>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white shadow-md">
        <div class="container mx-auto p-4 text-center text-gray-900">
            <h2 class="text-2xl">
                Don’t risk embarrassment about the condition of your property. Don’t allow yourself to be frustrated by trash pile-up,
                odor, high prices for frequent trash removal, and unresponsive service.
            </h2>

            <div class="flex justify-center py-6 space-x-6">
                <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                    Call Us
                </a>
                <a class="button" href="/contact/">
                    Get Information
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>